cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Talos, please cite it as below."
title: "Talos: an eval-driven, domain-transferable AutoResearch framework"
abstract: >-
  Talos packages community best practices for autonomous, agentic ML
  research-and-experimentation ("AutoResearch") as portable skills for coding
  agents (Claude Code, OpenAI Codex). It is eval-driven by design and built to
  transfer across domains, with autonomous driving and robotics as its first
  two instantiations.
type: software
authors:
